name: Non Sponsored Families
query:
select center,region,father,tabSponsorship.start_date,tabSponsorship.end_date
from tabFamily
join tabSponsorship on tabSponsorship.family = tabFamily.name
where tabFamily.name not in 
    (select tabFamily.name from tabFamily
    join tabSponsorship on tabSponsorship.family = tabFamily.name 
    where tabSponsorship.start_date <= %(date_on)s
    and %(date_on)s <= tabSponsorship.end_date)
group by father
